		<section id="HA899063EE5654F3C839BBE4C7EB91545" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Permanent deduction for mortgage insurance premiums</header>
			<subsection id="H0F834665B0F646298E6F38B58DA92CE5">
        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>In general</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">
          <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:163/ss:h/p:3/sp:E">Subparagraph (E) of <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/26/163">
            section 163(h)(3)
          </external-xref> of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986</cato:entity-ref> is amended by striking
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:163/ss:h/p:3/sp:E/cl:iv">clause (iv)</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="HECF8275328674AA29846CBDB66B37224">
        <enum>(b)</enum>
        <header>Effective date</header>
        <text>The amendment made by this section shall apply to amounts paid or accrued after December 31, 2013,
			 and to amounts properly allocable to periods after such date.</text>
			</subsection>
